parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "OaAnEx.Leave them. We can take them on our own.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx.They won't be unarmed for long. This was our one chance! Why the hell didn’t you shoot them, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.We’re doing this the right way. Now look for a way out.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Shut up! When this is over, we’ll all be heroes and you’ll be a free woman.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnDeNo1.Shit! This day just keeps getting better and better.");
